{{Otheruses|night flower}}
The '''Tarkenian Nightflower''' was a type of [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] [[Foodstuff/Legends|beverage]]<ref name="RebelDawn">''[[Rebel Dawn]]''</ref> that originated in<ref name="Planetnamia">{{Planetnamia|other=the Tarkenian Nightflower|system=[[Tarkenia system/Legends|Tarkenia system]]|legends=1}}</ref> in the [[Tarkenia system/Legends|Tarkenia system]] of the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories']] [[Karthakk sector/Legends|Karthakk sector]].<ref name="EAOC">{{SW|url=news/star-wars-the-essential-atlas-online-companion|text=''Star Wars: The Essential Atlas'' Online Companion|int=Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion}}</ref>

{{Food-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The Tarkenian Nightflower appeared in ''[[Rebel Dawn]]'', [[A. C. Crispin]]'s [[1998]] third novel in [[The Han Solo Trilogy (hardcover)|''The Han Solo Trilogy'']].<ref name="RebelDawn" />

